cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.NE 

The paper is about facial landmark detection using a novel local detector that combines neural architectures and mixtures of experts. This falls under computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG) sub-categories. The paper also proposes a new algorithm that uses this local detector, which involves optimization and modeling techniques (cs.AI). The paper uses publicly available datasets to evaluate the performance of the proposed method, which falls under multimedia (cs.MM) and neural networks (cs.NE) sub-categories.
